IN RE: COMMITTEE ON BAR ADMISSIONS CFN-534568 NO. 2019-BA-0291 Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 22, 2019

ORDER

Treating petitioner's "Request for Written Reasons" as a petition for reconsideration of this court's February 22, 2019 order,

IT IS ORDERED that reconsideration be and hereby is denied.

JOHNSON, C.J., would grant.

Hughes, J., would grant.
